OL,5,G0315 Ramsay's Kitchen Nightmares USA
OL,6,     FPark's Edge: In Atlanta, Gordon
OL,7,     Fhelps first-time restaurant owners
OL,8,     FRichard and Jorge, whose
OL,9,     Festablishment is in trouble due to
OL,10,     Ftheir constant fighting, poor food
OL,11,     Fand bad vibes.
OL,12,G0405 Four in a Bed
OL,13,     FThe competition kicks off at The
OL,14,     FRichard III in Middleham, where
OL,15,     FKen and Sharon introduce the group
OL,16,     Fto their racehorse Rosairlie.
OL,17,     FThere's just one problem: guest
OL,18,     FMatt is afraid of horses.
