OL,5,G0430 Four in a Bed
OL,6,     FKeith and Lisa Shearin host at the
OL,7,     FCourt House Unique Boutique B&B in
OL,8,     FShelsley Walsh, Worcestershire.
OL,9,     FSome of their guests are blown
OL,10,     Faway by the rooms, but trouble
OL,11,     Fbrews over their rates.
OL,12,G0500 Four in a Bed
OL,13,     FJo and her son Louis host at
OL,14,     FCastley Camp in Otley, Yorkshire.
OL,15,     FKen and Sharon are horrified by
OL,16,     Fstains on their bedding and the
OL,17,     Fdust in the room, and Jo is left
OL,18,     Ffuming over the feedback.
