OL,5,G0525 Four in a Bed
OL,6,     FThe last visit is to the Lion &
OL,7,     FSwan in Congleton, where owner
OL,8,     FPaul and manager Matt go all out
OL,9,     Fto win. But Lisa and Keith are
OL,10,     Fshocked by their waterbed and
OL,11,     Fdirty bathroom.
OL,12,G0555 Four in a Bed
OL,13,     FIt's the final day of the
OL,14,     Fcompetition and the B&Bers meet
OL,15,     Ffor the last time to find out how
OL,16,     Fmuch they've been paid and to
OL,17,     Fsettle some scores, before the
OL,18,     Fwinner is announced.
